# VLAN DNS Testing Checklist

Use this checklist to verify DNS resolution via Pi-hole + Unbound on each VLAN.

✅ Pi-hole DNS is now fully working on VLAN 30 (192.168.30.x)

✅ Queries resolve quickly and correctly.

✅ DNSSEC is working.

✅ Blocklists are functioning.

✅ Queries are reaching Pi-hole (and responses are getting back).

